casebody.data:
Thursday, December 24, 1992

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

91-1763. Toledo Bar Assn. v. Sanders.

This cause came on for further consideration upon respondent’s request for stay of suspension. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, effective December 22, 1992, that said request for stay of suspension be, and the same is hereby, denied, in that all filings relating to this matter have been submitted to and considered by the court before the court issued its disciplinary entry on December 11, 1992.

Douglas, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., dissent and would grant the stay.
